sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant WebApp as Library Web App
    participant API as Library REST API

    User->>WebApp: Search for book (e.g., "1984")
    WebApp->>API: GET /books?query=1984
    API-->>WebApp: 200 OK, [Results]
    WebApp-->>User: Display search results

    User->>WebApp: Borrow book (Book ID: 123)
    WebApp->>API: POST /borrow { bookId: 123, userId }
    API-->>WebApp: 200 OK, Borrowed confirmation
    WebApp-->>User: Show borrow success

    User->>WebApp: Return book (Book ID: 123)
    WebApp->>API: POST /return { bookId: 123, userId }
    API-->>WebApp: 200 OK, Return confirmation
    WebApp-->>User: Show return success